@node not03 "UGN ANNOUNCES HENRY CHUNG AS ASIA COORDINATOR"

@{B}UGN @{UB}ANNOUNCES @{I}HENRY CHUNG @{UI}AS ASIA COORDINATOR
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

@{I}FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE@{UI}

Contacts:
@{I}Wayne Hunt@{UI}, @{B}UGN @{UB}Executive Director - @{I}wayne@amiga.org@{UI}
