@{B}TWISTER PPC @{UB}TURBOBOARD
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

@{B}TITAN COMPUTER @{UB}proudly presents the new @{B}Twister G3/G4 PPC @{UB}Project

The Story so far....

The  @{B}Twister G3/G4 @{UB}project for @{B}Amiga 1200 @{UB}is a cooperation between @{B}ACT @{UB}(@{B}Apollo@{UB}),
@{B}Haage&Partner @{UB}and @{B}Titan Computers@{UB}.

The  new  @{B}Motorala  G3/G4  PPC@{UB}-Cpu`s open a new world of speed and creativty for
@{B}A1200 @{UB} users.  With  a  @{B}Twister  PPC @{UB} board  the  @{B}Amiga  1200 @{UB}will play again in
champions-league  of  powerful  computer  systems.  Old @{B}68k @{UB}times are over a new
RISC-CPU era has begun.

Due  to  @{B}Haage&Partners  68k @{UB} emulation  which  is  fit  in  a  2MB Flashrom the
@{B}Twister-PPC @{UB}board reaches a 100% compatiblity to old @{B}68xxx @{UB}CPU`s.

The  emulation is powerful enough to reach the speed of an @{B}68060 @{UB}Cpu on a 300Mhz
@{B}G3 @{UB} turbo  board.  Furthermore  the @{B}Twister PPC@{UB}-board has 2 local @{B}PCI@{UB}-Slots with
each  100  mhz  bus  clock.  The Slots are suitable for a 2d/3d graphic board on
@{B}RivaTnT2 @{UB}basis and for @{B}Ultra-Wide-SCSI @{UB}controller.

The  @{B}Twister @{UB} boards  will  need a lot of space therefore it could only fit in a
@{B}Amiga 1200 @{UB}tower system.

Specifications:
  * @{B}G3/G4 PPC@{UB}-board with 300 - 450 MHz
  * 2 local @{B}PCI@{UB}-Slots with each 100 Mhz Bus clock
  * 2 Ram slot for upto 512MB SG-Ram, also clocked with 100MHz
  * 512 kb 2nd Level Cache
  * 2MB Flashrom for BIOS and @{B}68k @{UB}emulation

Suggested retail price for @{B}G3 @{UB}300Mhz version DM 1100.- (incl. 16% local taxes)

Expansion boards:

  * @{B}Twister@{UB}-Vision
      * 2D/3D graphic board with 8MB SG-Ram, upgradeable to 16MB
      * @{B}Riva TNT2 @{UB}graphic chip.
      * @{B}Amiga @{UB} signal  will be passed through the gfx-board. No Monitor switcher
        or something else needed.
    suggested retail price DM 349.- (incl. 16% local taxes)

  * @{B}Twister@{UB}-SCSI
      * @{B}UW-SCSI@{UB}-controller.
      * upto 20MB/sec transfer rate.
      * DVD-Support.
